<p>Challenges like knowing if you can go on holiday for two weeks without having to check your email every five minutes. What to do if your team members and you always differ on what is important. And what if you and your team face the same issues over and over again? Is there a good way to discuss performance and personal issues openly? How do you have a better relationship with your employees?</p>

<p><strong>People don't quit their job, they quit their boss. First you grew. Now you lead.</strong></p>

