<p>Stretch will feature innovative, resourceful, and inspirational leaders sharing their real world stories on their success (and sometimes their failures). They will talk about the challenges of building successful teams and leading organizations. Get inspired by stories from companies that have got the most out of the people that work for them in the face of every conceivable (and inconceivable) challenge out there.</p>

<p>A conference for everyone that wants to connect with the people behind the curtain and learn more about the tools of a successful manager. Join our conference to connect with this and the next generation of leaders who are struggling with the same problems that you are. Once you’ve found each other, there’s a chance you might find some solutions too.
